! Keymap updates for Crouton (Ubuntu 14.04 chroots in ChromeOS).  This currently
! swaps the left control and the super key to reduce strain on one's pinky.

! remove the "control" and "super" modifiers from the left control and super
! keys, respectively.
remove mod4    = Super_L
remove control = Control_L

! add the modifiers to the left super and control keys, respectively.
add control = Super_L
add mod4    = Control_L
